author: Screen Junkies
description:
Before Freakier Friday zaps into theaters, revisit the original film that feels like it probably should have stayed on the Disney Channel. Not that that’s necessarily a bad thing! We F with The Suite Life, and this one is good as far as body switch comedies go! It’s just, like, man did parts of this not age well, and I’m not talking about Lindsey Lohan. You’ll see…

Comment below with who YOU’D like to switch bodies with in an early 2000’s PG comedy

Voice Narration: Jon Bailey the EPIC VOICE GUY (@epicvoiceguy on all socials)
